text:
{
  "prompt": "An advanced electric scooter design concept featuring a liquid cooling system. The scooter is streamlined and sporty, inspired by models like the Yamaha XMAX 250. It includes visible technical elements such as a radiator with cooling fan near the front, coolant hoses leading to a central battery pack and motor, and a compact DC brushless water pump. The battery pack is mounted low in a skateboard-style platform. The scooter has a modern step-through frame, front telescopic suspension, dual rear shocks, disc brakes with ABS, and large 15-inch front and 14-inch rear wheels. The cooling system includes a visible translucent coolant reservoir and heat-dissipating aluminum fins. Background is a clean design studio environment with technical blueprint sketches in the background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital illustration of a futuristic electric scooter styled after the Yamaha Maxam, featuring a streamlined, low-slung body. The design integrates a liquid-cooling system with visible blue-highlighted components such as a front-mounted radiator, side coolant reservoir under the seat, and tubing leading to the mid-mounted electric motor. The scooter has a long, wide seat, large front fairing, and enclosed rear wheel cover. Modern urban styling, grayscale body with blue cooling system highlights.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic digital illustration of an electric delivery bike inspired by the attached photo. It should keep the compact, step-through frame style, deep blue color, and upright seating position. Add a sleek integrated battery within the frame, rear cargo box in black, and subtle branding on the side similar to 'BURCHDA'. Emphasize clean lines, delivery utility, and urban mobility while preserving the original bike's proportions and practicality. Render it in a bright outdoor urban setting.",
  "referenced_image_ids": ["file-BRDXRgD8yJgVRK1vSpadM1"]
}

{
  "prompt": "A digital illustration of an electric scooter without exterior cowls, exposing the internal frame and structural components. The frame resembles a step-through design with visible welded tubes, inspired by the compact and upright geometry of small electric bicycles. The frame is painted blue and includes mounting points for a rear delivery box and battery pack under the central floor. The front fork, handlebar, suspension, and mid-drive motor are all exposed, showing a mechanical and practical style.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A detailed technical side-view line drawing of an electric scooter frame, without body panels (no cowl), showing the internal structure and components such as motor, radiator, and battery. The front wheel is 20 inches and the rear wheel is 16 inches. The seat includes a clear ergonomic backrest for lower back support. The drawing uses precise black lines on a white background, emphasizing the mechanical frame, suspension, and proportions.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A quarter-class electric motorcycle inspired by the geometry and proportions of a cruiser-style bike like the Honda Fury. The design features a low-slung frame, long front fork with a relaxed rake angle, large 21-inch front wheel and smaller 16-inch rear wheel, and a matte olive green finish. The motorcycle is equipped with a visible central motor and battery pack instead of a traditional engine, and it includes a minimalist seat and no rear fender. The overall style blends classic chopper aesthetics with modern electric components, shown in a clean digital illustration on a white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
